{
  "stem": "24111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- suddenly, during the night, we were standing on the balcony, and we say-- we saw on-- on one mountain, fires, and then on the second one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next day, we heard this farmhouse was burned by the-- by the Italian troops, because they had supported the partisans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this house was burned by the partisans, because this farmer sold food to the Italians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were more or less in the middle of-- and the fighting starting to-- getting worse by day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And finally, one day, the partisans came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Joschko, of course is fluent in-- in the Yugoslavian language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- he told them about the-- about our situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were very supportive about us, more so when they heard that we were not friendly with the Germans at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they thought German-- they didn't understand Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For them, Jews was-- what is a Jew?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they knew we were German or we were Austrian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally, they realized that we-- we were persecuted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they brought us food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then a friendlier relationship started to begin with the partisans, with Cernij, their leader.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cernij, that was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is not easy for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is S-Z-R-N-Y.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think there's a thing like this on top of the S or something, Cernij.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the meantime, the Italian troops, in the same area, found out that the partisans are in the area too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started to make sweeps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came also to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, are the partisans in this area?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, of course, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, a matter of fact, one day, we had a wounded partisan hiding upstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
